==Documentation==
This template creates a full accessory page layout with hero section, tabs, wiki content, and sidebar.
Uses Semantic MediaWiki for structured data storage and display.

Accessories are gaming peripherals and hardware - controllers, headsets, cables, etc.

===Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
|| Name || Display name of the accessory
|-
|| Guid || Giant Bomb API identifier
|-
|| Aliases || Alternative names (comma-separated)
|-
|| Image || Accessory image filename
|-
|| Deck || Short description shown in hero
|}

===Usage===
<pre>
{{Accessory
| Name = DualShock 4
| Guid = 3000-123
| Deck = The wireless controller for the PlayStation 4...
}}

== Overview ==
Your wiki content here...

{{AccessoryEnd}}
</pre>
